00:21:07,800 --> 00:21:12,620
 It says this, grace and peace to you from God our Father

428
00:21:12,620 --> 00:21:15,960
 and our Lord Jesus Christ, who gave himself for our sins

429
00:21:15,960 --> 00:21:18,320
 to rescue us from the present evil age

