00:22:38,640 --> 00:22:40,920
 with continuing to live the Christian life

461
00:22:40,920 --> 00:22:44,500
 because we live by the grace and mercy of God.

462
00:22:45,520 --> 00:22:47,560
 And we continuously need it.

